text: Işın Karaca (born in London, United Kingdom, on March 7, 1973) is a Turkish- Cypriot pop singer. She has released four music albums. These are: Anadilim Aşk, İçinde Aşk Var, Başka 33/3 and Uyanış. Her fourth album means Awakening in English language. She also has been an actress for the film Sen Ne Dilersen. == Other websites == * Official web site of Işın Karaca * Işın Karaca Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Turkish singers Category:Singers from London
